snippet.title: Don Duality - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Don Duality – AVAILABLE NOW!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2247570/Don_Duality

Prepare yourself for an immersive dive into Chaos Manager, a captivating card-based game set in a world of pixel art and a mafia parody backdrop.

Deploy your gangsters for daring heists, and master the art of money laundering within the confines of your own restaurant empire. 

As you hire and manage your staff, and push for establishment upgrades, always bear in mind the analogy to a roulette wheel – for in Don's journey, life is just as unpredictable.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/don_duality
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@dondualitygame
